  "text": "Cytoplasmic calcium elevation was measured as described previously [CITATION_1] . Aequorin-expressing transgenic seeds were grown on a one-half-strength MS medium for 4 d. A single seedling was incubated in 200 mL of one-half-strength MS medium supplemented with 2.5 mM coelentrazine cyclopentyl (Sigma) for 16 h. Bioluminescent emission was recorded for 150 s with a Techan plate reader (Tecan). For experiments with reduced PMF, the assay medium was modified by adding 100 mM KCl or adjusting the pH to 7.5.",
